name: Surreal Unicorn Dreams
description:
Sometimes the colors in our dreams make many thing seem surreal. Adding a beautiful unicorn to the mix enhances the experience!

The unicorn is a symbol of hope, insight, and high ideals. They also represents gentleness, power, and purity. In a dream, it suggests magical feelings or a wish for more magic and enchantment in your life. It can also mean that you or someone you know is a person of purity and innocence with high personal standards.
